skills.name: Gale
skills.description: [SP: 20][CD: 25s] Releases a tornado traveling in a zigzag path, sending enemies along the path airborne and dealing 82 Ice DMG multiple times. Enemies hit will suffer 80% slower Move Speed and Attack Speed for 1.54s.
